msgstr "常规"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/generations.phtml:23
msgid "Generations"
msgstr "代"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/display.phtml:78
msgid "Hide empty segments"
msgstr "隐藏空白扇段"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/page.phtml:80
msgid "Hide more options"
msgstr "隐藏更多选项"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:65
msgid "Hide the PNG export button"
msgstr "隐藏 PNG 导出按钮"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:56
msgid "Hide the SVG export button"
msgstr "隐藏 SVG 导出按钮"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:102
msgid ""
"How much of each place is shown in chart arcs — the full name, only the "
"lowest levels, or the place combined with its country as a name or ISO code. "
"Users toggle place visibility on/off in the chart form."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/display.phtml:59
msgid ""
"Images are only shown if the arc segment is wide enough. Images for "
"descendants are not yet available."
msgstr "仅当弧段足够宽时才显示图片。后代的图片尚不可用。"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/page.phtml:41
msgid "Individual"
msgstr "个人"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/details.phtml:34
msgid ""
"Inserts the GEDCOM NICK value in quotes between the given names and the "
"surname (e.g. Martin \"Chalky\" White). Mirrors the legacy webtrees "
"behaviour for trees that store nicknames in the separate GEDCOM NICK field."
msgstr ""
"将 GEDCOM NICK 字段的值用引号插入在名字与姓氏之间（例如 Martin \"Chalky\" "
"White）。模拟旧版 webtrees 的行为，适用于在单独的 GEDCOM NICK 字段中保存昵称"
"的家谱。"

#: src/Configuration.php:427
msgid "Lowest level (e.g. parish)"
msgstr "最低层级（如教区）"

#: src/Configuration.php:429
msgid "Lowest three levels"
msgstr "最低三个层级"

#: src/Configuration.php:428
